sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant Webhook as ODH Model Controller<br/>Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Controller as ODH Model Controller<br/>Reconcilers
    participant MR as Model Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>80/443/TCP
    participant Client as External Client

    Note over User,Client: Flow 1: InferenceService Creation and Route Provisioning

    User->>K8s: kubectl create InferenceService<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (user)
    K8s->>Webhook: POST /mutate-serving-kserve-io-v1beta1-inferenceservice<br/>mTLS (client cert)
    Webhook-->>K8s: Mutated ISVC (defaults applied)

    K8s->>Webhook: POST /validate-serving-kserve-io-v1beta1-inferenceservice<br/>mTLS (client cert)
    Webhook-->>K8s: Validation response (allow/deny)

    K8s-->>User: InferenceService created

    Note over Controller: Watch event received

    Controller->>K8s: GET InferenceService<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
    K8s-->>Controller: InferenceService spec

    Controller->>K8s: CREATE Route<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
    Controller->>K8s: CREATE NetworkPolicy<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
    Controller->>K8s: CREATE ServiceAccount<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
    Controller->>K8s: CREATE Role/RoleBinding<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
    Controller->>K8s: CREATE ServiceMonitor<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
    Controller->>K8s: CREATE PodMonitor<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)

    alt Model Registry Enabled (MODELREGISTRY_STATE=managed)
        Controller->>MR: POST /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/registered_models<br/>Auth: Bearer Token<br/>TLS 1.2+ (skip verify option)
        MR-->>Controller: Model registered
    end

    Controller->>K8s: UPDATE InferenceService status<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)

    Note over Client,Router: Flow 2: Inference Request via Route

    Client->>Router: POST /v1/models/model:predict<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (optional)
    Router->>K8s: Forward to predictor service<br/>HTTP 80/TCP or HTTPS
    K8s-->>Router: Prediction result
    Router-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over User,Controller: Flow 3: NIM Account Creation

    User->>K8s: kubectl create Account (NIM)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (user)
    K8s->>Webhook: POST /validate-nim-opendatahub-io-v1-account<br/>mTLS (client cert)

    Webhook->>K8s: GET Secret (API key)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
    K8s-->>Webhook: NGC API Key

    Note over Controller: NIM Account Controller activated

    Controller->>K8s: GET Account CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
    K8s-->>Controller: Account spec with API key reference

    Controller->>K8s: GET Secret (NGC API key)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
    K8s-->>Controller: API key value

    Controller->>NGC: GET /v2/org/{org}/models<br/>Auth: NGC API Key<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP TLS 1.2+
    NGC-->>Controller: Model list

    Controller->>NGC: POST /v2/org/{org}/secrets<br/>Auth: NGC API Key<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP TLS 1.2+
    NGC-->>Controller: Pull secret data

    Controller->>K8s: CREATE Secret (pull secret)<br/>Type: kubernetes.io/dockerconfigjson<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
    Controller->>K8s: CREATE ConfigMap (model config)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
    Controller->>K8s: CREATE Template (runtime)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)

    Controller->>K8s: UPDATE Account status<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
    K8s-->>User: Account ready
